1
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:12,400
Your Highness is a noble prince.

2
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:16,010
How could you possibly understand

3
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:19,000
my inner suffering?

4
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,840
I used to have parents and brothers.

5
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:27,079
And I lived a peaceful and happy life.

6
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,920
It was Qi Beiyi

7
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:35,480
who betrayed his country for glory,

8
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:39,720
making me watch my own family

9
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:42,200
die tragically right in front of me.

10
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:46,720
I only wanted this traitor

11
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,880
to get the retribution he deserved.

12
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:54,010
I would never hurt anyone else.

13
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:59,120
If my father hadn't insisted on starting a war,

14
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:02,480
how could Qi Beiyi have committed treason?

15
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:05,920
Those innocent people in Xuecang

16
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:08,520
wouldn't have lost their lives either.

17
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:09,680
Ultimately,

18
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:13,000
all of this was caused by my father.

19
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:15,930
Hiding this from Your Highness until now,

20
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,680
I am ashamed.

21
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,960
Now that I have made a grave mistake,

22
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,760
I don't expect Your Highness to forgive me.

23
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:25,760
I

24
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,840
am at Your Highness's disposal.

25
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,920
At my disposal?

26
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,090
Alright.

27
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,770
Then I shall sentence you to death.

28
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,000
With the traitor eliminated,

29
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,960
I die with no regrets.

30
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:48,680
No regrets?

31
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,460
Your Ladyship.

32
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:07,880
The First Prince just woke up

33
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:09,480
and went to visit Ling Xuele.

34
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,240
Right now,

35
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:12,160
he has gone to see His Majesty.

36
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:12,960
Perhaps

37
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:15,170
he's going to plead for Ling Xuele.

38
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,920
I thought Yunchuan

39
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,890
was someone immune to persuasion.

40
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,440
I didn't expect

41
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,440
him to be such a romantic.

42
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,040
Then again,

43
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,680
this Ling Xuele

44
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:28,040
did a pretty good job.

45
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,720
After all, we've trained her for so long.

46
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,720
Abandoning her for nothing

47
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:32,760
would be a pity.

48
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,220
Your Ladyship.

49
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:36,560
You know His Majesty's temper.

50
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,980
How could he let someone go so easily?

51
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,520
Then I

52
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:44,960
will just go with the flow.

53
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,160
I will plead with my father

54
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,220
to spare your life,

55
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:15,600
in exchange for your help fulfilling one of my wishes.

56
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,330
Do you agree?

57
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,460
Your Highness.

58
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:21,040
What wish can I help you with?

59
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,760
You want to deal with Consort Yu.

60
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:27,880
My birth mother's difficult labor

61
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,940
has everything to do with Consort Yu.

62
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,320
Consort Yu will be on guard against you from now on.

63
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:33,880
If she really finds out something,

64
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,210
you will certainly die.

65
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:37,800
I have a way to make her lower her guard

66
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,920
and trust you more.

67
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:45,440
It turns out everything I did

68
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,930
couldn't be hidden from the First Prince.

69
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:50,040
How did he know?

70
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:21,280
I'll go get the medicine for Your Highness.

71
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,280
Stop right there.

72
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:26,960
Right now, you are no longer some Xuecang princess.

73
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:28,720
If you still have some conscience,

74
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,120
stop playing tricks.

75
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:33,640
I, Ling Xuele,

76
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,840
am not an ungrateful person.

77
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,660
Your Highness.

78
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,380
Your Highness.

79
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,580
The medicine is ready.

80
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,180
You are still injured.

81
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:40,120
You should go back and get some rest too.

82
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,050
I'll go back and rest

83
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,440
after His Highness falls asleep.

84
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:46,920
Okay.

85
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,580
Your Highness, you're awake.

86
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,570
Did you stay here all night?

87
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:25,600
Your Highness got hurt because of me.

88
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,520
It is only right for me

89
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,130
to take care of you here.

90
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,450
You've worked hard.

91
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,810
Go back and get some rest early.

92
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:37,520
Yes.

93
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,300
Your Highness.

94
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,880
I have a favor to ask.

95
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,280
What is it?

96
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,080
I know

97
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:55,010
this request is somewhat inappropriate,

98
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:57,040
but I want to ask that traitor in person

99
00:09:57,040 --> 00:09:59,000
why he betrayed Xuecang.

100
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:11,640
Take it.

101
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:21,180
Thank you, Your Highness.

102
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,810
His Majesty has ordered

103
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,500
that you be beheaded in public tomorrow.

104
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,480
If you speak any more nonsense,

105
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,880
I'll tear your mouth off.

106
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,520
You...

107
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,690
I'm here to question him

108
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,160
on the First Prince's orders.

109
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:47,240
Please let me pass.

110
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:48,040
Yes.

111
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:58,540
So it's you, the remnant of the Snow Kingdom.

112
00:10:58,800 --> 00:11:00,920
Aren't you afraid I'll report you?

113
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:04,000
Who would believe the words of a treacherous person

114
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,960
like you?

115
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:07,000
You brought this

116
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,280
upon yourself.

117
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:10,450
How on earth did you escape,

118
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:13,040
and how did you get into this Yunqiu Palace?

119
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:15,400
Of course, the souls of thousands of Xuecang people

120
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,560
protected me to get here,

121
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:19,360
to take the life of an unrighteous person like you.

122
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:22,060
All of us in Xuecang are loyal and righteous.

123
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:24,240
How could there be such a treacherous person like you?

124
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,520
Only the living

125
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,940
have the right to talk about loyalty.

126
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:30,480
So what if I betrayed Xuecang?

127
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,320
You...

128
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:36,200
You deceived the ruler and betrayed your ancestors.

129
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,680
Don't you feel guilty towards

130
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:39,240
the tens of thousands of soldiers,

131
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,640
and the tens of thousands of innocent Xuecang people

132
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:41,760
who died?

133
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:45,200
Xuecang's fall was inevitable.

134
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,760
It was a foregone conclusion.

135
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:47,920
Even without me,

136
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,450
within three years,

137
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:51,690
Yunqiu would have conquered Xuecang.

138
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:54,440
With the King of Yunqiu's temperament,

139
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:56,680
those people wouldn't have escaped death anyway.

140
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:57,440
Besides,

141
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,840
since ancient times, who doesn't serve the strong?

142
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:02,100
What is there for me to feel guilty about?

143
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,240
A person like you

144
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:08,080
deserves to suffer the death of a thousand cuts.

145
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:08,840
It's a pity

146
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,380
I can't kill you with my own hands.

147
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:34,760
Little Pingle, are you still mad at your father?

148
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:37,120
I hate Father.

149
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,520
Let me ask you,

150
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:46,240
why did Father punish you today?

151
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:49,440
Because I talked back to my teacher.

152
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:52,460
Since you were in the wrong first,

153
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:55,160
why were you unwilling to accept the punishment?

154
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:57,080
Because Father shouldn't have

155
00:12:57,080 --> 00:13:00,560
punished me in front of so many servants,

156
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:03,120
letting them laugh at me.

157
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:05,840
I am a princess of this country, after all.

158
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:07,360
Pingle.

159
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:10,720
The status of a princess is indeed noble.

160
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:13,250
But you should understand,

161
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:16,900
while the royal family enjoys the reverence of the people,

162
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,520
our every word and action

163
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,880
should serve as an example to them.

164
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:23,320
If

165
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:26,880
your father turns a blind eye to your mistake today,

166
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:29,840
if others make mistakes in the future,

167
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:32,320
can they also escape punishment?

168
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:39,640
Mother,

169
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:45,720
I will go to Father later and accept my punishment.

170
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,480
I knew it.

171
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:52,280
Our Pingle is the most sensible.

172
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:57,080
Look at what I brought you.

173
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:00,920
Snowflake crisp.

174
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:05,560
Is it good?

175
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:15,680
Thank you, Mother.

176
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:17,920
Eat up.

177
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:21,360
Pingle.

178
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,500
Father, Mother, you're here.

179
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,300
Look at my writing.

180
00:14:28,560 --> 00:14:29,560
Does it look good?

181
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:33,040
This girl's handwriting

182
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:34,370
has improved somewhat.

183
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:35,260
Not bad.

184
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:36,820
Thank you, Father.

185
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:38,720
But

186
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,940
the strokes are still a bit rough.

187
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:41,440
You

188
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,360
should spend more time tempering

189
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,000
your mind.

190
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:49,400
I think

191
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,060
Pingle wrote it very well.

192
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,560
Your father is being too strict.

193
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:54,520
Exactly.

194
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:55,730
Father, Mother.

195
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:58,560
I insisted on seeking revenge,

196
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:00,400
and almost caused a disaster.
